ED_Title: Election of the Executive Director of the United Nations Human Settlements Programme (UN-Habitat)
ED_DecisionText: At its 55th plenary meeting, on 20 January 2022, the General Assembly, on the proposal  of the Secretary-General,  (footnote: See A/76/638.) re-elected Maimunah Mohd SHARIF  (Malaysia) as Executive Director of the United Nations Human Settlements Programme (UN-Habitat) for a term of office beginning on 20 January 2022 and ending on 19 January 2024.
ED_Disclaimer: The final text of this decision will be contained in document A/76/49 (Vol. III) after editorial review.
